ActNunavut Act
SubjectTransfer to the Commissioner of Nunavut ( approximately 6.12 hectares)
PrecisOrder transfering to the COMMISSIONER OF NUNAVUT, in perpetuity, the administration and control of several surveyed parcels of land comprising the beds of bodies of water (approximatively 6.12 hectares), within the municipal boundaries of the hamlet of Arctic Bay.
